title: My Love from Another Star
description:
According to actual Joseon records, in the year 1609 a shining unidentified object flew through the skies overhead, startling and confusing the citizens. 400 years later, Do Min Jun, one of the passengers of the strange craft, still lives in Seoul, a genius and powerful alien among average humans. Meanwhile famous celebrity actress Cheon Song I faces scorn from netizens who find her airhead behavior annoying, while she herself still wonders about the strange man who stopped time to save her from certain death years ago. As a comet approaches Earth that can bring Min Jun back to his home planet, the two cross paths once again.
